---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const lang = 'en';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<BaseLayout title="Legal Notice" lang={lang}>
  <div class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8">Legal Notice</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-12">Last updated: May 2026</p>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-muted leading-relaxed">
      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">1. Business Information</h2>
        <p>In compliance with Law 34/2002 on Information Society Services and Electronic Commerce (LSSI), we provide the following information:</p>
        <ul class="list-none space-y-1 mt-3">
          <li><strong>Business name:</strong> Henna By Hanazz</li>
          <li><strong>Contact email:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@smgtec.es" class="text-gold underline">info@smgtec.es</a></li>
          <li><strong>Location:</strong> Barcelona, Spain</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">2. Terms of Use</h2>
        <p>By accessing and using this website, you accept the following terms:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 mt-2">
          <li>All content on this website (text, images, designs) is the intellectual property of Henna By Hanazz unless otherwise credited.</li>
          <li>You may not reproduce, distribute, or modify any content without prior written permission.</li>
          <li>Pexels images used on this site are licensed for free commercial use with attribution as required.</li>
          <li>We reserve the right to modify or discontinue services without prior notice.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">3. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>Henna By Hanazz is not liable for damages arising from the use of this website or from temporary unavailability due to technical issues beyond our control. We make every effort to keep the site operational but cannot guarantee uninterrupted access.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">4. External Links</h2>
        <p>This website contains links to external sites (Instagram, WhatsApp, Google Maps, Stripe). We are not responsible for the content or privacy practices of these third-party sites.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">5. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>These terms are governed by Spanish law. Any disputes shall be submitted to the courts of Barcelona.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
